   1:tools/fsr_reader.cpp **** /**
   2:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  * fsr_reader.cpp — FSR pressure sensor reader on ADC1
   3:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  * Daisy Seed
   4:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  *
   5:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  * Reads an FSR connected to A1 (ADC1 / D16 / pin 23) and prints raw ADC,
   6:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  * voltage, percent, and a bar to the serial monitor at ~10 Hz.
   7:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  *
   8:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  * Typical wiring (voltage divider, higher pressure → higher reading):
   9:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  *   3.3V ── FSR ── A1 ── 10kΩ ── GND
  10:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  *
  11:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  * Inverted (higher pressure → lower reading):
  12:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  *   3.3V ── 10kΩ ── A1 ── FSR ── GND
  13:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  *
  14:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  * Open `screen /dev/tty.usbmodem* 115200` to view.
  15:tools/fsr_reader.cpp ****  */
